gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 118, Magic 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Clippers defeated the Magic, 118-102. Paul George recorded 27 points, seven assists, and seven rebounds for the Clippers, with Russell Westbrook adding 18 points, seven assists, and six rebounds in the victory. Paolo Banchero tallied 15 points, four rebounds, and four assists for the Magic in the losing effort. The Clippers improve to 3-1 on the season, while the Magic fall to 2-2.
